dBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T18:06:49.000Z","msg":"想支持<br />\n但冇我教果科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"無問題，好快你會見到呢堆分類！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfVvLjBuQcnbgLw566DLQKWvX4ZHTPNbtZh68d7gRKnHq?filename=LFOfTCJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFOfTCJ.png&h=4b2c2743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n交了給apple 審批，如無意外明天會有得更新<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEcon 同個bug 要下一轉update🙏🙏"},{"pid":"e0ed2460dc555c470bf4d86de1349f656242a8c1","tid":2449822,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T00:06:25.000Z","msg":"咁啱想搵學生<br />\n之前個中介食水勁深<br />\n要比頭一個月半份糧佢<br />\n多謝ching"},{"pid":"66e54d303e671ac335ed48a866c51f15b255adf3","tid":2449822,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T00:24:06.000Z","msg":"描述嘅字數可唔可以改短啲<br />\n打曬所有科成績都未夠40字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a129a8bf25a626e4b79081129d6d4b266434a0","tid":2449822,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9607be7862e743355460f135f1fe5e63a998717f","tid":2449822,"uid":349349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"我講多少少自己背景<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係獨立寫app Programmer,  靠寫app 賺下錢，有時補下習，教下琴。<br />\n<br />\n呢個app,  同任何機構都無關係（除左賣google 廣告）<br />\n<br />\n黎緊搵宣傳公司幫手宣傳，係自己俾錢搵人去同家長宣傳，無同咩補習社合作，亦無外判。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T00:28:07.000Z","msg":"G持"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d36c85cb17da7632df4b04e5b3b23c036e8a2a05","tid":2449822,"uid":349349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"感謝大家一路支持，我都會繼續努力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一直研究班中介嘅玩法，現實始終有啲野要面對<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班人，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">用緊各位導師嘅錢去賣廣告吸引家長</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMrxovV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMrxovV.png&h=2cc89f70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFx8GhA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFx8GhA.jpg&h=eb60116f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個循環，令好多家長用佢地個，逼大家都要用佢地先有學生，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">最後俾佢地抽水</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要打破呢個循環， 要各位家長們都使用免抽水App  例如快搜補補。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會係四月搵公司去進行宣傳，App 內賺到嘅錢都會拎去做宣傳，務求更多家長使用。<br />\n<br />\n另外希望各位導師都教育下家長，用免抽水app 搵導師， 同俾個rating 快搜補補， 只要上要榜首，我嘅宣傳會更有效！<br />\n<br />\n快搜補補"}}